notes.annotations: After adding pharmaceutical forms it was discovered that this patient received Cisplatin and Pemetrexed 2 months prior to the TCGA cancer procurement.

Patient was diagnosed 2 years prior to cancer procurement with no surgery until TCGA tumor was resected, therefore this may be considered a progression.  Patient was treated with pleurodesis more than 90 days prior to cancer procurement which is acceptable.
category.annotations: Item may not meet study protocol

notes.annotations: During Enrollment it was found that the patient received raditiaion treatment 2 months prior to TCGA tumor procurement.
